ActFederal Real Property and Federal Immovables Act
SubjectOrder declaring that certain buildings in the real estate portfolio of the Department of National Defence are no longer necessary for the defence of Canada
PrecisOrder declaring that all federal properties located at Canadian Forces Base Kingston, the Royal Military College of Canada at Kingston and other locations in the Kingston surrounding area are deemed no longer necessary for the defence of Canada.
